--- !u!114 &2655943682800173565
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 6724986343879956388}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fbeb6d65be27d3b40a131a1e4ace56b5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  steps:
  - message: "Hey, Gizmo i'm back! Why those dunes ahead don\u2019t look straight-line
      anymore?"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Welcome back, {player}! Ahh that\u2019s because you\u2019ve entered
      the world of two-dimensional motion. Here, both x and y directions come into
      play."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: So now my hovercraft moves horizontally and vertically?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Precisely. Think of your motion as a combination \u2014 one part forward,
      one part upward.."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "So that\u2019s why controlling my jumps over ramps feels harder..."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Right. Each jump forms a trajectory \u2014 a curved path made from
      both horizontal and vertical components."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 1
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Like forming a triangle between the two directions?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 1
    endTime: 2
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Correct! Velocity now has two parts: Vx and Vy. And the resultant velocity,
      VR, comes from both.  \r\n   VR\xB2 = Vx\xB2 + Vy\xB2."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 3
    endTime: 4
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Oh, like Pythagoras in motion. That\u2019s cool!"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 4
    endTime: 5
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Exactly. Angles are your key here.  \r\nSine gives vertical ratio,
      cosine gives horizontal ratio, and tangent gives slope."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 6
    endTime: 7
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "So my jump\u2019s angle determines how high or far I go?"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 7
    endTime: 8
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: You got it. Control the launch angle and both components, and you control
      the entire arc.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Sounds like I\u2019m steering a flying triangle now."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "(laughs) In a way, yes. Keep your horizontal speed steady and manage
      your vertical thrust. That\u2019s how you\u2019ll land cleanly."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Alright, Gizmo. Let\u2019s see if I can make a perfect jump this time."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Simulation initializing\u2026 trajectory test begins in 3\u2026 2\u2026
      1\u2026 go!"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
